title: Ash vs Evil Dead is DONE
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: To be honest I think that season 3 was meant to be the final season. With the Dark Ones killing Ruby, it looks like she's dead for good now. And Ruby is a main character, and It took her 3 seasons to actually, truly die. I hope Kelly survives at least, but it wont be surprising if she's dead for good too. I hope I didn't spoil anything for people who didn't watch last 9 episodes of season 3(sorry if I did)
Hail to the king baby...give me some sugar. Bruce quit not Stars
description:
It's official, Ash vs Evil Dead won't be getting a new home. #AshvsEvilDead #STARZ
